Step in and have a seat to remove your shoes before previewing this beautiful home. There will be pull over protection for your feet. From the great room you can take in the breathtaking gourmet kitchen with stainless steel appliances along with a cozy living area complete with an electric fireplace. Upstairs you will find 3 adequate bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with dark wood cabinets and cultured marble tops and, for your convenience, the laundry is located upstairs.
